            <div class="service-title">Cost Consultancy Services</div>
            <div class="service-desc">Accurate budgeting, cost evaluation, value engineering, and commercial assurance that protects your financial investment throughout the project lifecycle.</div>
            <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0 0 20px;font-size:.87rem;color:var(--text-muted);">
              <li class="d-flex gap-2 mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill" style="color:var(--accent);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;"></i> Cost Planning &amp; Budget Development</li>
